<p><strong>Damage Immunities</strong> cold, fire</p>

<p><strong>Senses</strong> darkvision 60 ft., tremorsense 60 ft.</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 5 (1,800 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Heated Body.</em></strong> A creature that touches the remorhaz or hits it with a melee attack while within 5 feet of it takes 7 (2d6) fire damage.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 20 (3d10 + 4) piercing damage plus 7 (2d6) fire damage.</p>

